IN RE ROCHELLE D.* (AC 26318)

Dranginis, Flynn and Dupont, Js.

Argued November 16 officially released December 6, 2005

In accordance with the spirit and intent of General Statutes § 46b-142 (b) and Prad ice Book § 79-3, the names of the parties involved in this appeal are not disclosed. The records and papers of this case shall be open for inspection only to persons having a proper interest therein and upon order of the Appellate Court.

 Per Curiam.

The judgment is affirmed.
